      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Kafka producer-ack SLO\n\n**Histogram:** `kafka_producer_request_latency_seconds_bucket` &nbsp; **Selector:** `{acks=\"all\",topology=\"intra_az\"}`\n\n**SLO:** 99.5 % of records acknowledged under **25 ms** p99 over the rolling 30-day window (ADR-0012 \u00a71, \u00a72.3).\n\nBurn-rate alert fires when the 1h burn rate exceeds **14.4\u00d7** and the 6h burn rate exceeds **6\u00d7** simultaneously (Google SRE multi-window recipe)."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "p50 (5m)",
      "description": "",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "datasource",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "datasource",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.5, sum by (le) (rate(kafka_producer_request_latency_seconds_bucket{acks=\"all\",topology=\"intra_az\"}[5m])))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 3,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
