      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error-budget burn rate (1h vs 6h)",
      "description": "Fraction of requests over the p99 bound in the chosen window. The two horizontal lines are the multi-window page thresholds (1h \u00d7 14.4, 6h \u00d7 6) from ADR-0012 \u00a73.",
      "datasource": {
